    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a donor car for parts. The engine struggles to stay running and the transmission slips significantly, indicating a need for major mechanical overhauls. Visually, the car has substantial rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn seats and a cracked dashboard. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
